{"name":"easyui-ext","tagline":"常用 easyui 扩展","body":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/test/css/style.css\">\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/res/easyui/themes/default/easyui.css\">\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/res/easyui/themes/icon.css\">\r\n\r\neasyui-ext 是一组 jQuery.easyui 的常用功能扩展集。目前已经实现了部分 validator 的规则，以及给 datebox 增加了基础的时间先后校验功能。\r\n\r\n1. 日期校验组建（datebox-validator）\r\n\r\n<div id=\"body\">\r\n\t<h2>Demo</h2>\r\n\t<label for=\"date-first\">Date first (After today):</label>\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<input id=\"date-first\" class=\"easyui-datebox\" validType=\"isAfter['@today','Today']\"/>\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<label for=\"date-second\">Date second (After data-first):</label>\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<input id=\"date-second\" class=\"easyui-datebox\" validType=\"isAfter['#date-first','Date first']\"/>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n比较从选择器选择的时间是否晚于今天：\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<input id=\"date-first\" class=\"easyui-datebox\" validType=\"isAfter['@today','Today']\"/>\r\n```\r\n\r\n比较从选择器选择的时间是否晚于另外一个日期：\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<input id=\"date-second\" class=\"easyui-datebox\" validType=\"isAfter['#date-first','Date first']\"/>\r\n```\r\n\r\n代码中的 `isAfter` 是自定义的验证规则，方括号内输入的第一个参数为选择器，第二个参数为提示消息中需要输出的日期的名称及描述。\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/res/easyui/jquery.min.js\"></script>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/res/easyui/jquery.easyui.min.js\"></script>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://raw.github.com/TeamImage/easyui-ext/master/src/js/validatebox/datebox.validate.ext.js\"></script>\r\n","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}